Hold it flat, Frankie!

698
01:12:58,643 --> 01:13:00,102
<i>He cannae hear you.</i>

699
01:13:03,440 --> 01:13:05,313
Sorry.

700
01:13:05,400 --> 01:13:06,978
I forgot.

