01:14:30,610 --> 01:14:32,354
<i>Hi, Frankie!</i>

707
01:14:33,488 --> 01:14:34,519
You well?

708
01:14:34,614 --> 01:14:36,571
Oh, no, thanks!

709
01:14:38,285 --> 01:14:39,483
Hello.

710
01:14:39,577 --> 01:14:40,740
Hiya.

711
01:14:40,829 --> 01:14:43,865
- You look nice.
- So do you.

712
01:14:47,252 --> 01:14:50,288
Oh, this is Ally, er... my partner.

713
01:14:50,380 --> 01:14:51,578
In crime.

714
01:14:52,757 --> 01:14:53,706
Hi.

715
01:14:56,344 --> 01:14:58,752
I thought you only had the one day.

716
01:14:58,847 --> 01:15:00,175
I did.

717
01:15:01,975 --> 01:15:03,469
This is the second half of it.

718
01:15:03,560 --> 01:15:05,683
Aye, Frankie must be delighted.

719
01:15:08,023 --> 01:15:09,766
So, what are you all up to now?

720
01:15:09,858 --> 01:15:12,100
Going home.
Frankie's got school in the morning.

721
01:15:17,324 --> 01:15:19,731
Why don't you stay?

722
01:15:19,826 --> 01:15:21,237
I mean, just for a wee while.

723
01:15:21,328 --> 01:15:22,703
<i>I mean, he'd love it.</i>

724
01:15:22,787 --> 01:15:26,832
Right, the DJ is rank,
but there's a great band on afterwards.

725
01:15:28,168 --> 01:15:30,789
No, sweetheart, it's been a long day.

726
01:15:30,879 --> 01:15:33,251
<i>And it's time to go now.</i>

727
01:15:33,340 --> 01:15:35,131
Come on, son.

728
01:15:35,216 --> 01:15:36,960
It's just this once.

